item.desc: Cologne was a total vibe! What a beautiful city to just walk around 💯 From the iconic Cologne Cathedral to the old cologne with cobblestone streets and Schokoladenmuseum, Cologne is a must-visit for anyone seeking a blend of history, culture, and delicious food. Alsoo had the best doner at Nimet Grill 🤤 #cologne #travel #traveltiktok #explore #europe #wanderlust #traveltok #fyppppppppppppppppppppppp
